Author: Arceliaz
Text: I’m sorry you’re going through this. It won’t always be this way I promise. ❤️

Author: toastedfingies
Text: Hey. I’m right here with you. We’ll get through this. Lately I have been throwing my food in the trash right away the moment I start thinking “why am i doing this???” sometimes I don’t get the feeling until after but if I can stop myself even once it helps me to stop myself twice the next day. I know morally it’s wrong but I can’t continue on at the rate I’m going either
